    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "-- SOLVED --\r\nJust noticed that there is a hit index inside the hit object as __hitIndex \r\n\r\nThus, the solution would be:\r\n\r\n```\r\nvar hitTemplate =\r\n  '<div class=\"hit\" id=\"{{__hitIndex}}\">' +\r\n   '<h1>#{{__hitIndex}}: {{ title }}</h1>'+\r\n  '</div>';\r\n```\r\n",
    "created_at": "2017-09-20T16:25:13Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2347#issuecomment-330906326",
